py failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104yde1665703073172.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/yde1665703073172.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/yde1665703073172.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"yde1665703073172\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Color Position\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Position of the color box in relation to the color name: <code class=\"ph codeph defvalue\">Left</code> (default) or <code class=\"ph codeph\">Right</code>.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"yde1665703073172__section_w793ab1b5b1_w794ab1b5_w795ab1\">\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"yde1665703073172__table_d12095e1_d12096e1_d12097e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"yde1665703073172__table_d12095e1_d12096e1_d12097e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Value</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"yde1665703073172__table_d12095e1_d12096e1_d12097e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Description</p>\n</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"yde1665703073172__table_d12095e1_d12096e1_d12097e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">(default)</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"yde1665703073172__table_d12095e1_d12096e1_d12097e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Color rectangle is displayed according to the definition in the\n                           application's <span class=\"ph filepath\">.ini</span> file.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"yde1665703073172__table_d12095e1_d12096e1_d12097e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">Left</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"yde1665703073172__table_d12095e1_d12096e1_d12097e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Color rectangle is displayed to the left of the color name.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"yde1665703073172__table_d12095e1_d12096e1_d12097e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">Right</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"yde1665703073172__table_d12095e1_d12096e1_d12097e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Color rectangle is displayed to the right of the color name.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"yde1665703073172__section_ct5_gfb_wwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d773903e145\">Applies To</h2>\n<p class=\"p\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"zfr1695290811319.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/zfr1695290811319.html\" title=\"Start the Microsoft Windows Color dialog box.\">colorbox</a></p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3617127\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3617127\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Color Position Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 10, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Color Position Position of the color box in relation to the color name: Left (default) or Right . Value Description (default) Color rectangle is displayed according to the definition in the application's .ini file. Left Color rectangle is displayed to the left of the color name. Right Color rectangle is displayed to the right of the color name. Applies To colorbox Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}